cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.AI, cs.DS

Reasoning: 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on privacy and proposes novel privacy mechanisms.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses sampling from an exponential family and specific generalized linear models, such as logistic regression.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper uses R\'enyi Differential Privacy (RDP) as a privacy definition.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes privacy mechanisms for machine learning models.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the impact of the prior distribution in mitigating the influence of individual data points.
